<p><div class="left-margin" id="set-C"><h2>Story</h2></div></p>

<p>Master and Mashu get sent to an idol Singularity. Being an idol represents the strength here. Ms Crane tried to save the master and mashu from a battle, but the attempt fails. E-chan is acting as an idol to save the master and Mashu. Then, they go to the living of E-chan together, to prepare turning a better idol.</p>

<p><img src="/img/fgo-waltz/a4.jpg" alt="Ms-Crane" /></p>
<div align="center">Ms Crane</div>

<p><img src="/img/fgo-waltz/a2.jpg" alt="E-chan" /></p>
<div align="center">E-chan</div>

<p>Then they hear the holy grail being available if they win the grail live competition. To obtain the invitation to the competition, they plan to challege the famous idol pair, with Medb and Tamamo cat.</p>

<p><img src="/img/fgo-waltz/a1.jpg" alt="Medb" /></p>
