<p><img src="/img/fgo-waltz/a3.jpg" alt="Tamamo-Cat" /></p>
<div align="center">Tamamo Cat</div>

<p>E-chan asks Medb and Tamamo cat to join the journey. A team borns here named AxXxS.</p>

<p><img src="/img/fgo-waltz/b1.jpg" alt="AxXxS" />
<img src="/img/fgo-waltz/b2.jpg" alt="AxXxS" /></p>
<div align="center">Form a new idol team "AxXxS"</div>

<p>As the new team, they start finding the next targets. The new competitors are Ushiwakamaru, Altera, Jeanne, and Helena. This team behaves as a group of actresses, instead of singing. AxXxS persists their way to perform, instead of following the style of their opponents, and then win the contest.</p>

<p><img src="/img/fgo-waltz/a11.jpg" alt="Ushiwakamaru" /></p>
