<div align="center">Helena</div>

<p>There is a hotel and holiday resort. Players can meet Nobu in summer outfit(musician?) there. Nitocris and Hassan of Serenity are the competitors this time. On the way, Medb gets hurt. She needs to spare the responsibilities of being a center, and find a new member for the team. For the result, Mashu joins the idol team, and E-chan gets trained to become a center. With the effort of the existing members, they are able to win the competition.</p>

