<p>The team AxXxS is finally able to enter the final round! They engage to compete the strongest idol group, with the members of Euryale, Shuten-douji, and Nero. It is interesting to see them just acting on their own performance, and their fans concentrate to support one of the three members. The whole concert still go well in this way.</p>

