<p>The team AxXxS manages to get the victory in the grail live! However, something strange happens, when another Ms Crane appears. Master and Mashu return to the beginning of the event. They decide to find out Ms Crane for more clues. Ms Crane finds her restriction, and try to break it. Then her memory returns. However, Medb and Tamamo cat have no memory of the journey of AxXxS anymore.</p>

<p>E-chan tries to fight against the another Ms Crane, and get the holy grail. Players can know the background of ŌĆ£thisŌĆØ Ms Crane, wanting to give return to her previous master. Her master passed away, and no one knew the talent of her previous master, of being good in design. She decided to hold events along with idols, and let them dress good in stage. Ms Crane along with master has the goal to seek for an idol with good potential to win in the grail live, and everything gets reset after the winner comes out. When master knows her intention, she/he suggests to hold an excellent stage, with all idols in this event, to farewell Ms Crane.</p>

